platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: Streets of Rage est de retour!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Catchy music, incredible combo-filled combat, co-op play, and a blast of nostalgic spirit ensures this classic brawling series still packs a punch.
